                      <a href="/UCIFund/About.php"><img alt="Because itâ€™s bigger than just us" src="/img/home/buckets/UCI_Fund_yellowb.jpg"/></a>
                      <p><strong>Because it&#8217;s bigger than just us</strong></p>
<p><em>Serving students across all schools, the UCI Fund provides the university with discretionary funds to support the areas of greatest need on campus and respond to new opportunities as they arise. Investing in the UCI Fund remains one of the most powerful ways in which you can help the university cultivate a dynamic learning environment for students and the community.</em></p>
