                                <div class="bucket">
            <h2 class="bucket-header">ZotFunder</h2>
                      <a href="https://zotfunder.give.uci.edu/"><img alt="Help make passion projects a reality" src="/img/home/buckets/zotfunder.jpg"/></a>
                      <p><strong>Help make passion projects a reality</strong></p>
<p><em>ZotFunder is a tool UCI students, staff and faculty can use to raise awareness and support for their ideas and passions. Whether it is producing a play, advancing a research endeavor or engaging in a novel activity, UCI&#8217;s new crowdfunding platform allows donors to give directly to a project created by a member of the UCI family. Create your own project or support an existing one today!</em></p>
<p><strong><a href=" https://zotfunder.give.uci.edu/">Learn more &#187;</a></strong></p>
